	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri scribebam non satis viribus instructus firmis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie in eodem luto haereo<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Vgl. <bibl>Adagia</bibl>, 1, 4, 99 (<bibl>LB</bibl> II 180).</note>; sed domini haec sunt opera, qui nos diligit etc.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hac hora cum hic cursor publicus roget, an aliquid <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Curiam</placeName> scribere velim, adferuntur literae in hanc sententiam: 2. mensis februarii tres <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italorum</placeName> cohortes a principe in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l631" cert="high">Burgundia</placeName> sunt interceptae et ad internecionem caesae.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rursum non procul Neviduno ad <placeName type="citizen_name">Ligerem</placeName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p17907">Gonzaga</persName>, ducis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1060">Mantuae</placeName> frater, beneficio reginae nostrae potitus abhinc biennium et filia et bonis ampliss[imi] ducis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1860">Nivernensis</placeName>, omnibus istorum Sodomitarum copiis praefectus, a <persName type="citizen_name">Condeis</persName> quoque interceptus est et gravissime sauciatus.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vulneratus tamen elapsus est; sed aiunt vix mortem evasurum et magnam editam istorum sceleratissimorum stragem.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduno</placeName> per dispositos equos ad eum et ad alios saucios missi sunt tres chirurgi, quibus se <persName type="auto_name">Edmundus ille Iesuita</persName> adiunxit, ut et animi et corporis medicos simul habeant.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Blesorum quoque oppidum (Bläß) constat a principe expugnatum, is est a parte aliqua <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l367">Aureliensis</placeName> praesidii.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fama quoque idem adfert de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1497" cert="high">Turonibus</placeName> et iam obsideri <placeName ref="l59" cert="high">Biturigas</placeName> (<placeName type="auto_name">Burges</placeName>) principe interim <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName> pergente.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed haec non ita certa ut superiora.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adrezzanus, Sodom[ita] <note>[eher: secundo]</note> iam apostata, <placeName type="auto_name">Costam</placeName>, oppidum ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l3048" cert="high">Rhodanum</placeName>, sola quadringentorum militum fortitudine communitum, post 3. oppugnationem tandem ingressus est, sed a <persName type="citizen_name">Condeis</persName> desertum, qui omnes cum incolis salvi sese in alium vicinum locum receperunt.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc ita male habuit ipsius milites, quasi illo conscio evasissent, ut seditione excitata dilapsae sint eorum copiae.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audisti procul dubio de immensa <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510">Turcarum</placeName> classe, qua cogitet <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName> invadere.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispania</placeName> accidit quiddam incredibile, sed tamen certissimum: <persName type="auto_name">Carolum</persName> cogitasse de patre <persName type="auto_name">Philippo</persName> interficiendo; sed filium nunc custodiri a patre.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">C[au]sa ignoratur adhuc; magnum infortunium.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec sic ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> scribuntur N 24. februarii.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ista communicare volui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Credite, quantum libet; ego sic illa, ut accepi, ad verbum recito.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta tres d. d.d. consules, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770">Carolum</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20473">Ganthnerum</persName>, <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontasellam</persName> et omnes amicos.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> sub vesperam 6. martii anno 1568.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Thobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fidelissimo ministro, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Chur.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
